---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="Contact Us | Free Resume Builder" description="Get in touch with the ResumeBuilder team. We're here to help with questions, feedback, or support.">
  <section style="padding:6rem 2rem 0;min-height:auto;display:block;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center">
    <div class="hero-split-content" style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center">
      <span class="eyebrow">Get in Touch</span>
      <h1>We'd Love to <span class="gradient-text">Hear From You</span></h1>
      <p>Have a question, suggestion, or need help? Send us a message and we'll get back to you within 24-48 hours.</p>
      <div class="hero-split-actions" style="justify-content:center">
        <a href="#form" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Send a Message</a>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Build My Resume</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="form">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="card card-elevated" style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.125rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:1.25rem">Send Us a Message</h2>
          <form onsubmit="event.preventDefault();Toast('Thanks for reaching out! We\'ll get back to you within 24-48 hours.','success');this.reset()">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="label">Your Name</label>
              <input type="text" class="input" required placeholder="John Doe" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="label">Email Address</label>
              <input type="email" class="input" required placeholder="john@email.com" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="label">Subject</label>
              <input type="text" class="input" required placeholder="How can we help?" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="label">Message</label>
              <textarea class="input" rows="5" required placeholder="Tell us more about your inquiry..."></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1rem;margin-top:1.5rem">
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Email</h3>
            <p>support@resumebuilder.com</p>
            <p>We respond within 24-48 hours</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4"/><path d="M12 8h.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Response Time</h3>
            <p>We aim to respond to all inquiries within 24-48 hours during business days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Feedback</h3>
            <p>Your feedback helps us improve. If you have suggestions for new features or templates, we'd love to hear them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-content">
      <article class="content-article">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Contact Questions</h2>

        <h3>Do I need an account to use ResumeBuilder?</h3>
        <p>No. ResumeBuilder requires no account, no sign-up, and no email. You can start building your resume immediately. Your data stays in your browser's local storage — it's never sent to our servers. This means your information stays private and you don't have to remember another password.</p>

        <h3>Is ResumeBuilder really free?</h3>
        <p>Yes, completely free. All templates, color themes, PDF export, AI writing tools, ATS scoring, and the cover letter generator are available at no cost. There are no hidden fees, no credit card required, and no limits on how many resumes you can create. We don't watermark your exports or lock essential features behind a paywall.</p>

        <h3>How is ResumeBuilder funded if it's free?</h3>
        <p>We include a few carefully selected affiliate links for products and services we genuinely recommend (like career coaching services and professional printing options). These partnerships help us cover hosting costs and development time without charging our users. We never recommend anything we wouldn't use ourselves, and our free tools will always remain free — affiliate revenue or not.</p>

        <h3>How do I export my resume as a PDF?</h3>
        <p>Once you've finished building your resume in our builder, simply click the "Download PDF" button. Your resume will be rendered as a clean, ATS-friendly PDF that you can submit to employers directly. The PDF preserves your chosen template design and color theme exactly as it appears on screen.</p>

        <h3>What if I find a bug or something doesn't work?</h3>
        <p>We actively maintain and improve ResumeBuilder. If you encounter a bug, formatting issue, or something that doesn't work as expected, please let us know through the contact form above. Include your browser name and version if possible, along with a description of what you were doing when the issue occurred. We typically resolve reported bugs within a few days.</p>

        <h3>Can I request a new template or feature?</h3>
        <p>Absolutely. We built ResumeBuilder for job seekers, and your input directly shapes our roadmap. If there's a template style you'd like to see, a feature that would make your job search easier, or an improvement to an existing tool, please reach out. We read every message and prioritize features based on how many users request them.</p>

        <h3>How do I check my resume's ATS score?</h3>
        <p>Visit our <a href="/ats-score">ATS Score Checker</a> page, paste or upload your resume text, and optionally add a target job description. Our tool will analyze your resume across 5 dimensions: keywords, formatting, contact information, section structure, and action verbs. You'll receive a score out of 100 with specific, actionable feedback for each category. You can make changes and re-check as many times as you need.</p>

        <h3>What browsers does ResumeBuilder support?</h3>
        <p>ResumeBuilder works on all modern browsers including Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge. The builder is fully responsive and works on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices. We recommend using the latest version of your preferred browser for the best experience. Internet Explorer is not supported.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-sm section-tools">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Free Career Tools</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="tools-grid">
        <a href="/" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Resume Builder</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/ats-score" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>ATS Score</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/cover-letter" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Cover Letter</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/resume-examples" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Examples</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/templates" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Templates</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 016.5 17H20"/><path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 014 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 016.5 2z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Blog</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="capture">
    <div class="capture-inner">
      <h3>Get Weekly Resume Tips</h3>
      <p>Join 10,000+ job seekers getting expert advice straight to their inbox.</p>
      <form class="capture-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault()">
        <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
        <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
      <p class="capture-note">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
